Sol,

What people usually do is that they pick the model with lowest AIC or BIC. If there is not much differences in AIC/BIC, there is not much difference in the models (and often even the curves look similar although they are found with different model equations). You better read on model selection with AIC/BIC.

Cheers, Jari Oksanen

